org.sql: SELECT issues.id FROM issues INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id INNER JOIN issue_statuses ON issue_statuses.id = issues.status_id LEFT OUTER JOIN custom_values AS cf_80 ON cf_80.customized_type = 'Issue' AND cf_80.customized_id = issues.id AND cf_80.custom_field_id = 80 AND 1 = 1 AND issues.tracker_id IN (SELECT tracker_id FROM custom_fields_trackers WHERE custom_field_id = 80) AND ((SELECT 1 FROM custom_fields AS ifa WHERE ifa.is_for_all = True AND ifa.id = 80) IS NOT NULL OR issues.project_id IN (SELECT project_id FROM custom_fields_projects WHERE custom_field_id = 80)) AND cf_80.value <> '' AND cf_80.id = (SELECT MAX(cf_80_2.id) FROM custom_values AS cf_80_2 WHERE cf_80_2.customized_type = cf_80.customized_type AND cf_80_2.customized_id = cf_80.customized_id AND cf_80_2.custom_field_id = cf_80.custom_field_id) LEFT OUTER JOIN users AS cf_80_user ON CAST(CASE WHEN cf_80.value = '' THEN '0' ELSE cf_80.value END AS DECIMAL(30, 0)) = cf_80_user.id WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'issue_tracking') IS NOT NULL AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13)) AND issues.is_private = False ORDER BY cf_80_user.firstname ASC, cf_80_user.lastname ASC, cf_80_user.id ASC, issues.id ASC LIMIT 1
